DocConstant.Name: CUT
DocConstant.Documentation: Excavation where soil or rock below topsoil is cut to the depth required for the construction of facilities such as roads and railways. The removed material can be used as fill ([<font color="#0000ff"><u>EarthworksElement</u></font>]($element://{04D59E49-786C-4558-8F2F-4AC00545AE17})) for embankments or to form a level surface on which to build.
